  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the fish balls and cook until browned on all sides.",
    "Add the noodles, fish sauce, soy sauce, calamansi juice, salt, and pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Cook for 2-3 minutes or until the noodles are well coated with the sauce.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy."
